    "(83)For the second term of (82), we take the expectationα k E ⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f ⊤ F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k) ⟩ = α k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k)] + α k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k)] = α k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k)] ≤ 2B F α k E[∥y k ∥∥∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ∥] ≤ 2B F L V V α k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ z k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω z k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ z k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B F L V V α k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B F L V V α k E[∥y k ∥] α k B F + ζ k B D + ξ k B H ≤ 2B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥] ≤ B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k,(84)where the fifth inequality follows from the step size condition ζ k ≤ ξ l ≤ α k, and the second equation follows fromE[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k)] = E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ E F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, a k, b k, s ′ k) -F (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k) | F k-1] = 0.The third term of (82) can be bounded similar to the first term,ζ k ⟨y k, ∇ ω V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f ⊤ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)⟩ ≤ L V ζ k ∥y k ∥∥ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)∥ ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 3L 2 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ D(ω k, µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k), V ϕω k,µ ⋆ (ϕω k) l)∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k) -D(ω k, µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k), V ϕω k,µ ⋆ (ϕω k) l)∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥∇ ω J l (ϕ ω k, µ) | µ=µ ⋆ (ϕω k) ∥ 2 + 12L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥μ k -µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k)∥ 2 + 12L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ Vl,k -V ϕω k,µ ⋆ (ϕω k) l ∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥∇ ω J l (ϕ ω k, µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k))∥ 2 + 12L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥μ k -µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k)∥ 2 + 24L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥V ϕω k,μ k l -V ϕω k,µ ⋆ (ϕω k) l ∥ 2 + 24L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ Vl,k -V ϕω k,μ k l ∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ε ϕ k + 36L 4 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ε µ k + 24L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ε V l,k,(85)where the fifth inequality follows from Assumption 6.For the fourth term of (82), we again take the expectation and use the technique in ( 84)ζ k E⟨y k, ∇ ω V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f ⊤ D(ω k, μk, Vf,k, s k, b k, s ′ k) -D(ω k, μk, Vf,k) ⟩ = ζ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k, s k, b k, s ′ k) -D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)] + ζ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k, s k, b k, s ′ k) -D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)] = ζ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ D(ω k, μk, Vl,k, s k, b k, s ′ k) -D(ω k, μk, Vl,k)] ≤ 2B D ζ k E[∥y k ∥∥∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ∥] ≤ 2B D L V V ζ k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ z k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω z k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ z k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B D L V V ζ k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B D L V V ζ k E[∥y k ∥] α k B F + ζ k B D + ξ k B H ≤ B D L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k.(86)For the fifth term of (82), recall the definition of π ⋆ in (2) and ( 4)ξ k ⟨y k, ∇ µ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f ⊤ H(π θ k, ω k, μk)⟩ ≤ L V ξ k ∥y k ∥∥ H(π θ k, ω k, μk)∥ ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 3L 2 V ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ H(π θ k, ω k, μk)∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ H(π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ω k, μk) -H(π ⋆ (ϕ ω k), ω k, µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k))∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥ H(π θ k, ω k, μk) -H(π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk), ω k, μk)∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k • L 2 H ∥μ k -µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k)∥ 2 + L 2 ∥μ k -µ ⋆ (ϕ ω k)∥ 2 + 6L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ∥π θ k -π ⋆ (ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2 ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 ∥y k ∥ 2 + 6L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ε π k + 12L 2 L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k ε µ k,(87)where the third inequality follows from the fact that H(π ⋆ (ϕ), ω k, µ ⋆ (ϕ)) = 0.Finally, for the last term of (82), we have in expectationξ k E[⟨y k, ∇ µ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f ⊤ H(μ k, sk) -H(π θ k, ω k, μk) ⟩] = ξ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ H(μ k, sk) -H(π θ k, ω k, μk)] + ξ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ H(μ k, sk) -H(π θ k, ω k, μk)] = ξ k E[⟨y k, ∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ⊤ H(μ k, sk) -H(π θ k, ω k, μk)] ≤ 2B H ξ k E[∥y k ∥∥∇ θ V π θ z k+1,ϕ ω z k+1, μz k+1 f -∇ θ V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f ∥] ≤ 2B H L V V ξ k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ z k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω z k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ z k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B H L V V ξ k E[∥y k ∥ ∥π θ k+1 -π θ k ∥ + ∥ϕ ω k+1 -ϕ ω k ∥ + ∥μ k+1 -μk ∥] ≤ 2B H L V V ξ k E[∥y k ∥] α k B F + ζ k B D + ξ k B H ≤ B H L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k.(88)Substituting ( 83)-( 88) into (82), we haveE[⟨ Vf,k -V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f + β k Ḡf (θ k, ω k, μk, Vf,k), V π θ k,ϕω k, μk f -V π θ k+1,ϕω k+1, μk+1 f ⟩] ≤ (1 -γ)β k 12 E[∥y k ∥ 2] + 6L 2 V α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[∥∇ θ J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2] + 6L 4 V α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V f,k] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k + (1 -γ)β k 12 E[∥y k ∥ 2] + 6L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε ϕ k] + 36L 4 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε µ k] + 24L 2 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V l,k] + B D L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k + (1 -γ)β k 12 E[∥y k ∥ 2] + 6L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε π k] + 12L 2 L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε µ k] + B H L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + B F L V V (B F + B D + B H)α 2 k ≤ (1 -γ)β k 4 E[∥y k ∥ 2] + 6L 2 V α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[∥∇ θ J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2] + 6L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε π k] + 6L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε ϕ k] + 36L 4 V L 2 D ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k + 12L 2 L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε µ k] + 6L 4 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V f,k] + 24L 2 V L 2 D α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V l,k] + L V V (B F + B D + B H) 2 α 2 k E[∥y k ∥ 2] + L V V (B F + B D + B H) 2 α 2 k ≤ (1 -γ)β k 2 E[∥y k ∥ 2] + 6L 2 V α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[∥∇ θ J f (π θ k, ϕ ω k, μk)∥ 2] + 6L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε π k] + 6L 2 V η 2 2 ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε ϕ k] + 16L 2 L 2 V L 2 H ξ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε µ k] + 6L 4 V ζ 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V f,k] + 24L 2 V L 2 D α 2 k (1 -γ)β k E[ε V l,k] + L V V (B F + B D + B H) 2 α 2 k,where the last inequality is due to the step size condition where 1(•) denotes the indicator function (1 if the condition holds, 0 otherwise).",
